title: Rigmar Radio Karaoke Collection 50900
description:
400 More Karaoke Classics under the letter T from the Rigmar 2015 collection.  The collection is up to date when posted and may contain one or more songs from 2016 in the ever popular CDG+MP3 format.

Note Rigmar has decided to stay with this format and not migrate to the new HD Video one due to file size considerations.   It is Audio quality which is more important on Karaoke not the Video output.

Note a major re organisation is taking place in this collection with the addition of multiple label choice on the more popular songs and this part of the collection has not been re visited as yet, so errors and duplications will be slightly higher in this half of the collection.

Rigmar Radio - Rockin' the Free World since 1967
